 description:
 'HVAC service techs in Las Vegas wear moisture-wicking polos for residential calls, Red Kap mechanic shirts for commercial work, and branded jackets for cool-morning installs. Here\'s the actual spec — what techs wear, what wears well in 130° attics, and how to brand it.',
